Sony's PlayStation 2 might have been discontinued earlier this year and their PlayStation Portable long been superseded by the PlayStation Vita in Europe, but there was still the occasional new game for both systems. Today marks the ends of this their era though with the final European release hitting the market - Pro Evolution Soccer 2014.
